assets.name: assets/e8V3ujtqq59
assets.description: This is a perfect starter for beginners to load up as an initial tool to help them see all of the brushes in front of them instead of having to remember what they look like by memory.  It also teaches you that when you remove white, it can dramatically affect the outcome of the stroke. White equals light, black equals darkness. Check it out!

assets.name: assets/8Vqsa-Z0JA5
assets.description:
Ashley Pinnick and I made a traditional painting setup of models from the Unity asset store, brought them into Tilt Brush like a traditional painting workshop.....  and tried painting them. Yay experiments!

We both had different thoughts of 2D or 3D, but similar approaches. This was hella experimental and hella fun. hahaha
